 />\n秘密會議有好多，Bilderberg Group係其中一個<br />\n<br />\n第一條片，Alex Jones係Bilderberg Group聚會外面受BBC記者訪問，<br />\nThe Answer To 1984 is 1776，1984指global tyranny，1776係美國立國，<br />\n喻意係堅守國家主權，立國理念，係對抗極權嘅方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二條片好詳盡解釋呢個全球權力網絡嘅陰謀，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個陰謀其實就係壟斷全球嘅資源同經濟運作，手段就係建立one world govt，<br />\n呢個陰謀已經有過百年歷史，要操縱全球資源，亦要控制全球人口，一係國家肯合作，唔肯合作，只有摧毀個國家，<br />\n發動戰爭係慣常手段，其他亦有Kissinger depopulation memorandum 200，取消現金用數碼貨幣做監控，一早已經講緊要microchip全球人口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n國家主權同全球管治(政府)之間嘅鬥爭，亦即係聯合國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAlex Jones同Aaron Russo比人叫右翼，係libertarian傳統，<br />\n主張小政府，個人權利至上，呢個係美國立國理念，亦即係nationalists<br />\n明白呢D背景，先知Donald Trump同緊咩人鬥，因為Trump都係個nationalists <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n撐Donald Trump嘅最好跟埋呢個The John Birch Society，<br />\n根據wikipedia：<br />\nTrump confidante and longtime advisor Roger Stone said that Trump's father Fred Trump was a financier of the Society and a personal friend of founder Robert Welch.[86] <br />\n <a href=\"https://jbs.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjbs.org%2F&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVEd%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=3756027b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://jbs.org/</a>"},{"pid":"e3c18daf70ac2cf656d6ad95a17e6aea71b0440c","tid":2281564,"uid":189875,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T16:47:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0fb80faf88801803da72a2820ccdaf2ccabf3e3b","tid":2281564,"uid":251026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T16:54:19.000Z","msg":"記者當面質問Kissinger關於depopulation嘅memorandum 200 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_d2bCirm6NA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_d2bCirm6NA&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy